      "rendered": "[Webinar Recording] Social Media for Nonprofits"
    },
    "content": {
      "rendered": "<p><strong>Presented: April 10, 2024</strong><br />\n<strong>Duration: 2 hours</strong><br />\n<strong>Cost: $30 (USD)</strong><br />\n<strong>Presented by:\u00a0<a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/heather-mansfield/\">Heather Mansfield</a>, Founder of Nonprofit Tech for Good</strong></p>\n<hr />\n<p>Social media is in a constant state of change and without regular education about emerging trends, your nonprofit could be wasting valuable time and resources implementing outdated best practices.</p>\n<p>From embracing Facebook &amp; Instagram Fundraising Tools to budgeting for social media ads,\u00a0<a href=\"https://buy.stripe.com/4gweYqe7HgGt1Hi6oF\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">this two-hour webinar</a>\u00a0will focus on what\u2019s new and next in social media so that your nonprofit can embrace being an early adopter. Topics include:</p>\n<p>\u2022\u00a0 Current best practices for using Facebook Pages and Instagram<br />\n\u2022\u00a0 What\u2019s new in Facebook and Instagram Fundraising Tools<br />\n\u2022\u00a0 How to effectively use LinkedIn Pages and Profiles<br />\n\u2022\u00a0 An introduction to Threads for nonprofits<br />\n\u2022\u00a0 Why nonprofits need a budget for social advertising</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"maxbutton-3 maxbutton maxbutton-buy-recording\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Buy Recording\" rel=\"noopener\" href=\"https://buy.stripe.com/4gweYqe7HgGt1Hi6oF\"><span class='mb-text'>Buy Recording</span></a></p>\n<hr />\n<p>This is the second webinar in a series of three required to earn a <a href=\"https://www.nptechforgood.com/earn-a-certificate-in-digital-marketing-fundraising-from-nonprofit-tech-for-good/\">Certificate in Digital Marketing &amp; Fundraising</a> from Nonprofit Tech for Good. To earn the certificate, you can attend the webinars live or view the recordings \u2013 or a combination of both.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.nptechforgood.com/earn-a-certificate-in-digital-marketing-fundraising-from-nonprofit-tech-for-good/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wp-image-37647 size-full aligncenter\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/2024-Certificate-in-Digital-Marketing-and-Fundraising-for-Nonprofits.png?resize=960%2C755&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"755\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/2024-Certificate-in-Digital-Marketing-and-Fundraising-for-Nonprofits.png?w=1000&amp;ssl=1 1000w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/2024-Certificate-in-Digital-Marketing-and-Fundraising-for-Nonprofits.png?resize=300%2C236&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/2024-Certificate-in-Digital-Marketing-and-Fundraising-for-Nonprofits.png?resize=768%2C604&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/2024-Certificate-in-Digital-Marketing-and-Fundraising-for-Nonprofits.png?resize=50%2C39&amp;ssl=1 50w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" /></a></p>\n<hr />\n",
